{"tid":2100643,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【我愛大陸煙】 國際控煙專家：港府禁止加熱煙 有違美國FDA決定及國際趨勢","createTime":"2020-07-09T07:56:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-09T11:10:26.000Z","uid":187028,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"bdc011e46898fcafc017fd6c61fa6a795b458cc5","tid":2100643,"uid":187028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T07:56:48.000Z","msg":"而家周街臭煙<br />\n隔住口罩都聞到臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n國際控煙專家今天呼籲特區政府參考美國食品及藥物管理局（FDA）最新決定，盡快批准加熱煙在本港售賣，及將產品視為緩減煙害的手段。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>FDA本週在其官方網站正式公佈，確認加熱煙IQOS為「風險改良煙草產品」(Modified Risk Tobacco Products)，並批准在全國進行銷售。</strong><br />\n<br />\nFDA煙草產品中心主任Mitch Zeller表示，FDA定性IQOS為「風險改良煙草產品」，是根據科學證據的支持。他引述申請者提交數據表示，使用IQOS可以幫助成癮的成年吸煙者減少甚至停止吸食傳統香煙，及減低其對有害化學物質的接觸，有關產品獲FDA認可主要是因為IQOS僅將煙草加熱，而非用火以高溫燃燒煙草，所產生的煙霧及有害化學物質大幅減少，顯著減低人體接觸15種特定有害及可能有害化學物質。<br />\n<br />\n亞太菸草減害倡議聯盟 Coalition of Asia Pacific Tobacco Harm Advocate (<a href=\"http://www.caphraorg.net\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.caphraorg.net&d=LWtkxptWC%2F4RDCuqQUibmur6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=4a916180\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.caphraorg.net</a>) 批評港府<strong>一刀切禁止所有新型煙草產品是妄顧科學的政策</strong>。CAPHRA專家顧問委員會由一些澳洲、新西蘭、新加坡、日本等關注煙害的醫療専家組成。這些國際專家指出，過去近十年各地專家的研究成果顯示，電子煙比傳統香煙危害大減。<br />\n<br />\n現時已有超過50個國家正式批准新型煙草產品銷售：包括英、美、加拿大、瑞士、德國、法國、意大利、日本、韓國、新西蘭等。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：熱血時報 - 加熱煙獲美國FDA認可 為風險改良煙草產品 <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/07-08-2020/64294\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F07-08-2020%2F64294&d=LWtkxptWC%2F4RDCuqQUibmur6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=5c7e67b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/07-08-2020/64294</a>"},{"pid":"2fc14c4f30334081f826de9ab2bd83cad3981421","tid":2100643,"uid":358233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T07:57:49.000Z","msg":"粗暴干涉內政"},{"pid":"4c7165f2b2b67132d7df7afa6f417eb66c7c709f","tid":2100643,"uid":315643,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T08:02:42.000Z","msg":"開埋加熱煙稅又得唔得<br />\n食埋fatfat<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bcf2143349a74214aad8ff8a19199c2c53cd97b","tid":2100643,"uid":315643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T08:12:27.000Z","msg":"而家外國加熱煙煙稅點計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20a8703032b260780e3eea2390cb97a14b5b8cbc","tid":2100643,"uid":22362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T08:42:54.000Z","msg":"電子煙要禁<br />\n真煙就唔洗"},{"pid":"2f8d2ab9619d4d9e4b1e752e78cec351f00123b5","tid":2100643,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"20a8703032b260780e3eea2390cb97a14b5b8cbc","tid":2100643,"uid":22362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T08:42:54.000Z","msg":"電子煙要禁<br />\n真煙就唔洗"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T08:46:57.000Z","msg":"稅+利益集團(例如煙仔何)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27e002b4ea5bb53506c2546f6c5a3b0b4dd3edbc","tid":2100643,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f8d2ab9619d4d9e4b1e752e78cec351f00123b5","tid":2100643,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"20a8703032b260780e3eea2390cb97a14b5b8cbc","tid":2100643,"uid":22362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T08:42:54.000Z","msg":"電子煙要禁<br />\n真煙就唔洗"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T08:46:57.000Z","msg":"稅+利益集團(例如煙仔何)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T11:10:26.000Z","msg":"枉香港人仲拎自由市場黎打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}